name: Glitched Reality - Divided We Fall
description: Reality of life if your living it in the 2021 Israel Gaza Conflict. Glitched Reality is soon to be all our realitys. So when eating your pancakes and drinking a extra large ice coffee this morning. Remember there are people all over the world waking up to nothing but death all around them. Pray for those involved in any wars. There is literally no attention being brought to the Israel Gaza Conflict - So Glitched Reality will keep bringing awareness.
